      "content": "wait really? i was kinda worried about getting withdrawal or anything since i've been on the zoloft for a few months now. are you sure it's safe to just stop it cold turkey and jump straight to the herb without like, tapering off first or anything? i don't want to mess up my brain chemistry or anything.",
